data.description: Rarely available 2 bedrooms, 2 bathroom Villa townhome in the highly sought after community of Villas on the Green is move-in ready. This lovely home features tile and wood flooring, an open kitchen with granite counters and upgraded wood cabinetry, and  stainless appliances. Single level living at it's best with two spacious bedrooms and two full bathrooms. Outside you will find a spacious screened in porch with garden views and easy access to the community pool. This home is conveniently located to great dining and shopping options and Easily accessible to major roadways and transportation. Low HOA. Don't miss this opportunity, homes don't come available often in this neighborhood!  Bring your offers today to make this dream home your own.
